namespace //github.com/robertbraeutigam/yaaml/

⟦public⟧
object YamlNull isa YamlValue ⁌
	A YAML null scalar. Produced by the core-schema resolution of
	plain scalars like <c>null</c>, <c>Null</c>, <c>NULL</c>, <c>~</c>,
	or an empty value. Canonicalises to <c>null</c> on display.
⁍ is

	⟦public⟧
	init () is
		pass
	end

	⟦public⟧
	⟦override⟧
	method display() → String is
		return “null”
	end

end object
